UDP  CS 模型
 

服务器：
  recv/send 只能用于TCP通信中替换read,write
  
  server:
      lfd = socket(AF_INET,SOCK_DGRAM,0)
      bind()
      while(1)
      {
        recvfrom()
        sendto()
      }
      close()

  client:
      connfd = socket(AF_INET,SOCK_DGRAM,0)    
      sendto(服务器地址，地址size); 
      recvfrom
      
      close()
